translations.5623862824135771507: The Lubumbashi Innovation Center, commonly known as Cinolu, is an innovation hub founded in 2015 in the city of Lubumbashi, DRC.
translations.6120690583137954424: We offer capacity building and support for early-stage businesses (startups and SMEs) through training, coaching, and mentoring, as well as incubation and consulting services. translations.3092774631341560909: Discover our story, our mission, and meet our dedicated team. We are passionate about what we do and committed to providing the best service possible.
